{
  "name": "Track crypto prices with HTTP / REST API and Slack hands-free",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "minutes",
              "minutesInterval": 30
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "08fef78d-9914-481f-99c0-c59d9db1e02c",
      "name": "Schedule Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.2,
      "position": [
        320,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "d377bbdf-39f1-40cf-ac7e-a1debad97251",
              "name": "receivedAt",
              "value": "={{ $now.toISO() }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "9aad91ff-ffbc-493c-b2b9-4a57eff1c48c",
              "name": "isValid",
              "value": "={{ $json ? true : false }}",
              "type": "boolean"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b7edb08b-b386-4e6b-85a9-2b82fc919f0c",
      "name": "Validate Input",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [
        560,
        300
      ],
      "notes": "Validate & normalize the input before downstream steps (§9.1)."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "url": "https://api.example.com/v1/data",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "bd53e233-3813-4360-856b-23f23600b936",
      "name": "Fetch Data",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [
        800,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "typeValidation": "loose",
            "version": 2
          },
          "combinator": "and",
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "e87f88b9-6a87-4fdf-b2e9-976f2bfe9f4a",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.amount }}",
              "rightValue": "open",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "dfab14d7-a37b-47d8-a44b-9719ebefb19d",
      "name": "Route on Condition",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        1040,
        300
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "message",
        "operation": "post",
        "select": "channel",
        "channelId": {
          "__rl": true,
          "value": "general",
          "mode": "name"
        },
        "text": "={{ $json.summary || 'New event' }}",
        "otherOptions": {}
      },
      "id": "3e69e1e9-df30-429b-a2ca-6a1ce8d2abd2",
      "name": "Send Slack Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.slack",
      "typeVersion": 2.2,
      "position": [
        1280,
        300
      ],
      "retryOnFail": true,
      "maxTries": 3,
      "waitBetweenTries": 2000
    },
    {
      "parameters": {},
      "id": "1d552f7a-aa66-4718-a4dd-d958956acfa7",
      "name": "Skip (No Action)",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.noOp",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        1280,
        500
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Track crypto prices with HTTP / REST API and Slack hands-free\n\n**Pattern:** Trading Alert\n**Trigger:** Scheduled\n**Integrations:** HTTP / REST API, Slack\n\nImport, add your credentials, then adjust parameters. Original FlowDex template.",
